snippet.title: Miro and The Flower of Youth - Indie Game REVEAL Trailer
snippet.description:
Introducing 'Miro and The Flower of Youth' – an indie RPG inspired by the Paper Mario Series! 

Want to support the Game? Subscribe! (It helps a lot!)

Join our Twitter and Discord for regular updates and communication!
https://twitter.com/miro_project

https://discord.gg/NPSCHa2jeH
